DESCRIPTION:<b>What</b>:<br>A 4-movie marathon. 1st movie is kid friendly\,
  second one is a comedy\, 3rd is scary\, 4th is truly terrifying.<br><br><b
 >When and Where</b>:<br>3 to ~11pm on Friday the 8th<br>High School Math Ro
 om<br> <br><b>Admission</b>:<br><ul><li>One ticket gets you in for as many 
 of the movies as you want to watch.</li><li>Ages 12 and under - $2 each<ul>
 <li>Must be accompanied by someone at least 16 y/o</li></ul></li><li>Ages 1
 3 to 18 - $5 (+ $1 for non students)</li><li>Ages 19+ $10 (staff get $2 dis
 count)</li></ul><b>What else</b>:<br>Food/Snacks will be sold at reasonable
  prices.
LAST-MODIFIED:20241029T134025Z
