DESCRIPTION:<span>We will be teaming up with pizza day once again for a fin
 al push to raise funds for Hurricane relief. Our last fundraising event wil
 l be a  </span><span><b>Hot Chocolate and Apple Cider Stand!</b></span><spa
 n><b> On Oct 31st\, </b></span><span>take the opportunity to eat your pizza
 \, lean into the chilly fall weather\, and warm up with a nice hot glass of
  Hot Chocolate or Apple Cider. Bring your pizza money and an extra </span><
 span><b>$2-3</b></span><span> to donate to Hurricane Relief in exchange for
  a cozy fall drink that not only tastes good\, but does good! One plain hot
  drink will be a $2 donation\, but you can add toppings such as carmel\, ex
 tra chocolate\, whipped cream\, and more for another $1 donation per toppin
 g :)</span>
LAST-MODIFIED:20241017T183429Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Cider/Hot Chocolate - Hurricane Relief Fundraiser
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
